"{\"uid\": \"arstechnica.com-ai-2024-07-dear-sydney-why-i-find-googles-ai-olympics-ad-so-disturbing\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Opinion: \\\"Help my daughter write a letter\\\" is not the same as \\\"Help me with boring busywork.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Opinion\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 7}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"boring busywork\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 91}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have watched any Olympics coverage this week, you have likely been confronted withan ad for Google's Gemini AI called \\\"Dear Sydney.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999999449301, \"rank\": 5.505718512088517e-10, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9995549436605711, \"rank\": 0.0004452545028316246, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any Olympics coverage\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"ad\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 189}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Dear Sydney\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In it, a proud father seeks help writing a letter on behalf of his daughter, who is an aspiring runner and superfan of world-record-holding hurdler Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999998198418487, \"rank\": 1.8002807708117343e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a proud father\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"an aspiring runner\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"superfan\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pretty good with words, but this has to be just right,\\\" the father intones before asking Gemini to \\\"Help my daughter write a letter telling Sydney how inspiring she is\\u2026\\\" Gemini dutifully responds with a draft letter in which the LLM tells the runner, on behalf of the daughter, that she wants to be \\\"just like you.\\\"\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999998198418487, \"rank\": 1.8002807708117343e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0634297377405423e-13, \"text\": \"LLM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"the father intones\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"Gemini\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"Gemini\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"a draft letter\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the runner\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"the daughter\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every time I see this ad, it puts me on edge in a way I have had trouble putting into words (thoughGemini itself has some helpful thoughts).\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ad\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"edge\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"some helpful thoughts\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As someone who writes words for a living, the idea of outsourcing a writing task to a machine brings upsome vocational anxiety.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"a living\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"a writing task\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"a machine\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"upsome vocational anxiety\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the idea of someone who's \\\"pretty good with words\\\" doubting his abilities when the writing \\\"has to be just right\\\" sets off alarm bells regardingthe superhuman framing of AI capabilities.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"his abilities\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"the writing\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"regardingthe superhuman framing\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think the most offensive thing about the ad is what it implies about the kinds of human tasks Google sees AI replacing.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999999449301, \"rank\": 5.505718512088517e-10, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most offensive thing\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"the kinds\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"human tasks\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"AI\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than using LLMs to automate tedious busywork or difficult research questions, \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" presents a world where Gemini can help us offload a heartwarming shared moment of connection with our children.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9995549436605711, \"rank\": 0.0004452545028316246, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LLMs\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"tedious busywork\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"difficult research questions\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"Dear Sydney\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"a heartwarming shared moment\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"our children\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a distressing answer to what's still an incredibly common question in the AI space: What do you actually use these things for?\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a distressing answer\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredibly common question\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marketers have a difficult task when selling the public on their shiny new AI tools.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1740, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marketers\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult task\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An effective ad for an LLM has to make it seem like a superhuman do-anything machine but also an approachable, friendly helper.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0634297377405423e-13, \"text\": \"LLM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An effective ad\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"an approachable, friendly helper\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An LLM has to be shown as good enough to reliably do things you can not (or do not want to) do yourself, but not so good that it will totally replace you.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0634297377405423e-13, \"text\": \"LLM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Microsoft's2024 Super Bowl ad for Copilotis a good example of an attempt to thread this needle, featuring a handful of examples of people struggling to follow their dreams in the face of unseen doubters.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Microsoft's2024 Super Bowl ad\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"Copilotis\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"a good example\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"this needle\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"examples\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"their dreams\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"unseen doubters\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Can you help me?\\\"\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"those dreamers ask Copilot with various prompts.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those dreamers\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"Copilot\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"various prompts\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I can help\\\" is the message Microsoft delivers back, whether through storyboard images, an impromptu organic chemistry quiz, or \\\"code for a 3D open world game.\\\"\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9999999988790478, \"rank\": 1.1205694455084523e-09, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"storyboard images\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"code\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2444}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3D open world game\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" ad tries to fit itself into this same box, technically.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" ad\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"this same box\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prompt in the ad starts with \\\"Help my daughter\\u2026\\\" and the tagline at the end offers \\\"A little help from Gemini.\\\"\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9995549436605711, \"rank\": 0.0004452545028316246, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prompt\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2567}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"the tagline\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"A little help\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you look closely near the end, you will also see Gemini's response starts with \\\"Here's a draft to get you started.\\\"\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"score\": 0.9995549436605711, \"rank\": 0.0004452545028316246, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Gemini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"a draft\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And to be clear, there is nothing inherently wrong with using an LLM as a writing assistant in this way, especially if you have a disability or are writing in a non-native language.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0634297377405423e-13, \"text\": \"LLM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"a writing assistant\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"this way\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"a disability\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"a non-native language\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the subtle shift from Microsoft's \\\"Help me\\\" to Google's \\\"Help my daughter\\\" changes the tone of things.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9999999988790478, \"rank\": 1.1205694455084523e-09, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the subtle shift\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"my daughter\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"the tone\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Inserting Gemini into a child's heartfelt request for parental help makes it seem like the parent in question is offloading their responsibilities to a computer in the coldest, most sterile way possible.\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gemini\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"a child's heartfelt request\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"parental help\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"the parent\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3181}, {\"ngram\": \"their responsibilities\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"a computer\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the coldest, most sterile way\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than that, it comes across as an attempt to avoid an opportunity to bond with a child over a shared interest in a creative way.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"a shared interest\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"a creative way\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one thing to use AI to help you with the most tedious parts of your job, as people do inrecent ads for Salesforce's Einstein AI.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3432, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 3518, \"end\": 3528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salesforce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.576867302429234e-29, \"text\": \"Salesforce\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salesforce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salesforce\"}, {\"begin\": 3531, \"end\": 3539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7440359406060996e-18, \"text\": \"Einstein\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Einstein\"}, {\"begin\": 3540, \"end\": 3542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"the most tedious parts\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3474}, {\"ngram\": \"your job\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"ads\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's another to tell your daughter to go ask the computer for help pouring their heart out to their idol.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"your daughter\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"the computer\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"their heart\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"their idol\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Google sees the message of the ad differently, of course.\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3651, \"end\": 3657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999999999449301, \"rank\": 5.505718512088517e-10, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3684}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe that AI can be a great tool for enhancing human creativity but can never replace it,\\\" Google spokesperson Alana Bealetold SFGate.\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3726, \"end\": 3728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2555925003147907e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"no